data.description: Your opportunity to own an all brick ranch home, in one of Berea's best subdivisions is here! This beauty sits in a cul- de- sac and is on nearly 1/2 acre lot! For starters, you are welcomed by a covered front porch. As you make your way inside, there you find a very large living room with vaulted ceilings and tons of natural light! As you make your way into the kitchen, you find custom cabinetry galore, as well as granite countertops and a magnificent built in custom pantry! There's nothing not to love about this kitchen! With a split bedroom layout, you have a full bath between the two guest bedrooms at one end of the home and a massive master, with walk-in closet and private bath, at the other end of the home for privacy. The utility room very spacious and great for  keeping your cleaning items organized. Speaking of storage, in the garage you have pull down stairs, for even more storage! This is a great neighborhood for walking, and enjoying the outdoors. You get all of this and are minutes to Interstate I-75 for your commute to work!
